.step
  h2 Color operations
  p.
    Operations against colors are especially useful.
    When adding or subtracting by a percentage the
    color lightness may be adjusted, or adjust the
    hue with <em>deg</em>:

  textarea.stylus
    body
      foo: white - 50%
      foo: black + 50%
      foo: #eee - #f00
      foo: #eee - rgba(black,.5)
      foo: #cc0000 + 30deg